[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1359},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":1335,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":1344},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1319,"date":1320,"description":18,"extension":1321,"lang":1322,"meta":1323,"navigation":801,"path":1324,"readingMinutes":1325,"seo":1326,"standalone":1327,"stem":1328,"tags":1329,"tldr":1332,"updated":1332,"url":1333,"__hash__":1334},"content\u002FNodejs\u002F超完整-Express-Imgur-套件上傳教學.md","超完整 Express Imgur 套件上傳教學","432259079",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1303},"minimark",[11,15,19,29,33,38,41,44,47,54,57,63,66,72,75,80,83,89,93,96,102,105,111,114,119,122,128,132,144,152,155,161,164,192,199,205,216,222,234,240,244,252,259,276,279,285,288,294,297,306,309,315,319,322,339,342,346,355,358,361,364,540,547,550,556,559,570,754,758,761,770,773,989,992,995,999,1002,1011,1014,1021,1030,1033,1240,1243,1246,1252,1255,1262,1269,1272,1299],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"Imgur 是一個非常好用的網路相簿服務，主要有提供免費的圖片儲存服務，開發上也可以拿來當作上傳練習，甚至是 Blog 文章的圖片儲存庫，所以這一篇就來分享一下在 Express 的 Imgur 的圖片上傳教學。",[20,21,22],"blockquote",{},[16,23,24,28],{},[25,26,27],"strong",{},"Note","\n本系列是針對 Imgur 來做介紹，但是 Imgur 在 2025 年 05 月 16 日之後限制台灣 IP 使用者無法上傳圖片，因此如果你是台灣使用者的話，可能會無法使用 Imgur 上傳圖片，這邊建議可以改用其他圖片上傳服務。",[12,30,32],{"id":31},"imgur-事前準備","Imgur 事前準備",[34,35,37],"h3",{"id":36},"imgur-album-建立","Imgur Album 建立",[16,39,40],{},"一開始先來學一下如何建立 Album，因此等一下後面上傳圖片都會指定到特定的 Album 中統一管理。",[16,42,43],{},"其實 Imgur 早期是可以直接建立一個 Album，但是後來不知道為什麼隱藏了 Album，按鈕並且非常難建立 Album，所以這一個流程基本上有八成以上的人找不到，所以會建議你務必依據以下流程來操作。",[16,45,46],{},"首先請你先登入 Imgur 網站，登入成功後點一下使用者列表中的「images」選項",[16,48,49],{},[50,51],"img",{"alt":52,"src":53},"images","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172151.png",[16,55,56],{},"接下來找到「All images」的下拉選單，裡面會有一個「New Album」點它",[16,58,59],{},[50,60],{"alt":61,"src":62},"New Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172202.png",[16,64,65],{},"會跳出一個關於 Album 相關的設定視窗，你就依照欄位填寫完畢之後按下 Save",[16,67,68],{},[50,69],{"alt":70,"src":71},"Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172203.png",[16,73,74],{},"新增成功之後你就會看到一片空白，因為當前顯示的 Album 是你剛剛新增的 Album，而我們並沒有新增任何圖片進去，自然就會是空的無誤",[16,76,77],{},[50,78],{"alt":70,"src":79},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.04.30.png",[16,81,82],{},"恭喜你這樣子就成功建立了一個 Album。",[16,84,85],{},[86,87,88],"del",{},"Imgur 的使用者體驗真棒",[34,90,92],{"id":91},"imgur-album-id-取得","Imgur Album ID 取得",[16,94,95],{},"由於我們稍後會需要將圖片上傳到特定 Album，所以會需要 Album 的 ID，因此請先點一下使用者列表的「gallery profile」",[16,97,98],{},[50,99],{"alt":100,"src":101},"gallery profile","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_08.png",[16,103,104],{},"接下來在右側找到「Albums」",[16,106,107],{},[50,108],{"alt":109,"src":110},"Albums","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_10.png",[16,112,113],{},"接下來就是點一下「Posts」=> 「All」，不意外第一個就是你剛剛建立的 Album",[16,115,116],{},[50,117],{"alt":70,"src":118},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_11.png",[16,120,121],{},"進入到 Album 之後你可以看一下它的網址，我們只需要下方圖片紅框圈起來部分就好，那部分就是我們要找的 Album ID，這邊就請先記憶著，稍後 Express 時會使用到",[16,123,124],{},[50,125],{"alt":126,"src":127},"Album ID","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_13.png",[34,129,131],{"id":130},"註冊-imgur-應用程式","註冊 Imgur 應用程式",[16,133,134,135,139,140,143],{},"接下來我們要來註冊一個 Imgur 應用程式，因為我們會需要 ",[136,137,138],"code",{},"client_id"," 和 ",[136,141,142],{},"client_secret"," 來上傳圖片，你可以點一下下方連結進入註冊",[16,145,146],{},[147,148,131],"a",{"href":149,"rel":150},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[151],"nofollow",[16,153,154],{},"進入之後你會看到這個畫面",[16,156,157],{},[50,158],{"alt":159,"src":160},"註冊","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.18.24.png",[16,162,163],{},"需要填寫的欄位如下",[165,166,167,176,184],"ul",{},[168,169,170,171],"li",{},"Application name\n",[165,172,173],{},[168,174,175],{},"任意名字",[168,177,178,179],{},"Authorization type\n",[165,180,181],{},[168,182,183],{},"選 OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL",[168,185,186,187],{},"Email\n",[165,188,189],{},[168,190,191],{},"聯絡你用",[16,193,194,195,198],{},"ps.如果你「Authorization type」是選「Anonymous usage without user authorization」的話，那「Authorization callback URL」就要填入「",[136,196,197],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com","」",[16,200,201],{},[50,202],{"alt":203,"src":204},"申請應用程式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_22.png",[16,206,207,208,139,210,212,213,215],{},"申請之後你會看到這個畫面，請記好你的 ",[136,209,138],{},[136,211,142],{},"，尤其是 ",[136,214,142],{}," 不可以搞丟，如果搞丟就只能重新生成而已",[16,217,218],{},[50,219],{"alt":220,"src":221},"申請成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_23.png",[16,223,224,225,227,228,233],{},"那麼這樣就申請完畢了，如果真的不小心遺失 ",[136,226,142],{}," 的話，可以點這個 ",[147,229,232],{"href":230,"rel":231},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002Faccount\u002Fsettings\u002Fapps",[151],"連結"," 到「Applications」中點一下「generate new secret」重新生成",[16,235,236],{},[50,237],{"alt":238,"src":239},"重新生成 client_secret","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_26.png",[34,241,243],{"id":242},"imgur-refresh-token-取得","Imgur Refresh Token 取得",[16,245,246,247,139,249,251],{},"前面我們已經準備了 ",[136,248,138],{},[136,250,142],{},"，但實際上還需要最後一樣鑰匙也就是 Refresh Token，而會需要 Refresh Token 是因為 Imgur 提供的 Token 是有時間限制的，那為了讓它可以自動刷新 Token，所以就必需要 Refresh Token 才可以。",[16,253,254,255,258],{},"取得 Refresh Token 的方式很特別，你需要將以下連結中的 「",[136,256,257],{},"${Client ID}","」換成我們剛剛申請的 Client ID",[260,261,266],"pre",{"className":262,"code":263,"language":264,"meta":265,"style":265},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Fauthorize?client_id=${Client ID}&response_type=token\n","html","",[136,267,268],{"__ignoreMap":265},[269,270,273],"span",{"class":271,"line":272},"line",1,[269,274,263],{"class":275},"sMAXC",[16,277,278],{},"然後貼到瀏覽器網址列上按下 Enter 送出",[16,280,281],{},[50,282],{"alt":283,"src":284},"網址列","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_30.png",[16,286,287],{},"這時候你會進入到一個警告畫面，只要確定這是你要用的應用程式就好，若沒問題就按下允許",[16,289,290],{},[50,291],{"alt":292,"src":293},"允許","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_31.png",[16,295,296],{},"允許之後你會被跳回 Imgur 的畫面，然後你把當前畫面的 Url 複製下來，基本上會這麼長",[260,298,300],{"className":262,"code":299,"language":264,"meta":265,"style":265},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002F#access_token=xxxxx&expires_in=xxxxx&token_type=bearer&refresh_token=xxxxx&account_username=xxxx&account_id=xxxx\n",[136,301,302],{"__ignoreMap":265},[269,303,304],{"class":271,"line":272},[269,305,299],{"class":275},[16,307,308],{},"但這邊注意看，我們只需要 Refresh Token 就好，把它記錄下來，稍後也會使用到",[16,310,311],{},[50,312],{"alt":313,"src":314},"Refresh Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_32.png",[12,316,318],{"id":317},"imgur-最後確認","Imgur 最後確認",[16,320,321],{},"最後這邊確定下流程，如果你有依照文章流程下來的話，你應該完成了以下動作",[165,323,324,327,330,333,336],{},[168,325,326],{},"建立一個空的 Album",[168,328,329],{},"取得 Album ID",[168,331,332],{},"取得 Client ID",[168,334,335],{},"取得 Client Secret",[168,337,338],{},"取得 Refresh Token",[16,340,341],{},"上述這幾樣基本上缺一不可，如果有缺少的話，可以再往前看一下 Imgur 流程。",[12,343,345],{"id":344},"express-imgur","Express Imgur",[16,347,348,349,354],{},"本身 Imgur 官方是有提供 API 可以給我們使用的，但是其實實際開發上如果有現成套件的話，基本上就會選擇用套件較快，而這邊我們會使用的就是「",[147,350,353],{"href":351,"rel":352},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.npmjs.com\u002Fpackage\u002Fimgur",[151],"Imgur","」這個同名套件，這邊我會區分成兩個版本提供範例程式碼。",[16,356,357],{},"Imgur 套件基本上有兩個版本，分別是 1.x 跟 2.x 的寫法，但大多網路上都是 1.x。",[34,359,360],{"id":360},"前端範例程式碼",[16,362,363],{},"而這邊前端範例程式都是如下參考，HTML 部分就不額外提供了。",[260,365,369],{"className":366,"code":367,"language":368,"meta":265,"style":265},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","const formData = new FormData();\n  formData.append('file-to-upload', e.target.form[0].files[0]);\n  axios.post('\u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Fupload', formData, {\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'multipart\u002Fform-data',\n    },\n  })\n  .then((data) => {\n    console.log(data)\n  })\n  .catch(error => console.log(error));\n","js",[136,370,371,394,424,441,447,462,468,474,499,511,516],{"__ignoreMap":265},[269,372,373,377,381,384,387,391],{"class":271,"line":272},[269,374,376],{"class":375},"sWyjQ","const",[269,378,380],{"class":379},"sCcAr"," formData",[269,382,383],{"class":375}," =",[269,385,386],{"class":375}," new",[269,388,390],{"class":389},"sj_SG"," FormData",[269,392,393],{"class":275},"();\n",[269,395,397,400,403,406,410,413,416,419,421],{"class":271,"line":396},2,[269,398,399],{"class":275},"  formData.",[269,401,402],{"class":389},"append",[269,404,405],{"class":275},"(",[269,407,409],{"class":408},"sTRMh","'file-to-upload'",[269,411,412],{"class":275},", e.target.form[",[269,414,415],{"class":379},"0",[2